Smart Technologies in Electric vehicles and Power grid

text.tspan: The objective of International Conference on Smart Technologies in Electric Vehicles and Power
Grid is to identify and explore the innovative research, current trends, technical support, security
solutions in the field of automotive systems and power grid. It also provides an opportunity to es
tablish a relationship and global engineering support for future collaboration. This international
conference offer a forum for the presentation of new advances and research results in the field of
Smart Electric Vehicles, Smart Grid, Smart devices, Hardware security, Smart Battery Management,
Data handling and Computation, Vehicular and grid Communications.
